<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ka Chenna Gam!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Suihlung a hel nin ka khawdak a,
 Lunglai nem a kim puou gam ngaih chu,
 Aw, ka chenna gam pawtsan ni hungtung intin
 Kahna bei tan a.

[V2]
 Aw, ka gam ngaih chu pakcha hawih in a bawm ie,
 Albang dah hin Na vanglim bel ka:
 Lalpa gam nuom ah ngabang leng ingka.

[V3]
 2. Nawp chang thei leng, chung leng van chang leng,
 Thangvan sanga lengin va chieh ka;
 Kalvari tang thing hansedawl chunga,
 Chun va chuong ingka.

[V4]
 3. Vangkhuo ah leng, leng lenguol ngaih tawh,
 Ka suihlung len puonbang a bang dem?
 Guol kim a lenin suihlung hel suhai puona,
 Kah lai hai puona.

[V5]
 4. Khaile, lunghel khuom bang do hitiu,
 Chung Pathien vangin chang bang dam leng,
 Lautha vangkhuo ah lai tuol leng khawm hitiu,
 Lei nungtieng sawn in.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>222</hymn_number>
</song>